data.name: Default Eeoc Data Request
data.description: This template is used for requesting EEOC data from the candidate.
data.html_body:
Thank you for your interest in {{JOB_NAME}} at {{COMPANY}}.

For government reporting purposes, we ask candidates to respond to the below self-identification survey. Completion of the form is entirely voluntary. Whatever your decision, it will not be considered in the hiring process or thereafter. Any information that you do provide will be recorded and maintained in a confidential file.

As set forth in {{COMPANY}}’s Equal Employment Opportunity policy, we do not discriminate on the basis of any protected group status under any applicable law.

Thank You

data.name: Default Request Interview with Calendly

data.html_body:
{{CANDIDATE_FIRST_NAME}},

data.name: Default Rejection Notification For Followers
data.description: This template is sent to all followers of a candidate when they are marked as rejected.
data.html_body: This is an automated message to alert you to a status change of {{CANDIDATE_NAME}}, a candidate whom you are following in Greenhouse. Please know that the hiring team has decided not to move forward with this candidate's application for {{JOB_NAME}}. Please be mindful that the candidate may not have been notified yet or could still be active on other roles. We recommend reaching out to the hiring team with any questions.

interview process.
data.html_body: {{CANDIDATE_NAME}}, whom you are following in Greenhouse, was moved into {{STAGE_NAME}} for {{JOB_NAME}} by {{ACTING_USER}}.

data.name: Default Event Prospect Auto Reply
data.description: This template is sent automatically to prospects after your recruiting event.
data.html_body:
{{CANDIDATE_FIRST_NAME}},

Thank you for attending {{EVENT_NAME}}. If you haven't already submitted a resume or would like to upload a high resolution version of your resume, you can do so here: {{RESUME_UPLOAD_LINK}}.

Regards,
{{COMPANY}}

** Please note: Do not reply to this email. This email is sent from an unattended mailbox. Replies will not be read.

data.name: Default Scorecard Reminder
data.description: This template is sent to users when they have a scorecard due.
data.html_body:
Hello,

It's been {{TIME_SINCE_INTERVIEWED}} since you completed your interview with {{CANDIDATE_NAME}}.

We know that feedback quality gets worse the longer you wait to submit. In fact, one hour after the event, memory recall declines to 44%.

Submit your feedback now to help us make the right hiring decision – {{SCORECARD_LINK}}

Your feedback is important! Thanks for your help.

data.name: Default Candidate Rejection
data.description: This template is sent to candidates when you reject them from a job.  You will always have the ability to preview, edit and customize this email before sending, or choose not to send it at all.
data.html_body:
{{CANDIDATE_FIRST_NAME}},

Unfortunately, we have decided not to proceed with your candidacy for the current opening at {{COMPANY}}.

We received many qualified applicants and have decided to move ahead with another candidate who we feel is a better match for this particular position.

Thanks again for your interest in {{COMPANY}} and we wish you luck in your search.

Regards,
{{COMPANY}}

data.name: Default Candidate Auto Reply
data.description: This template is sent automatically to candidates when they complete your online job application, letting them know that you've received their application.
data.html_body:
{{CANDIDATE_FIRST_NAME}},

Thanks for applying to {{COMPANY}}. Your application has been received and we will review it right away.

If your application seems like a good fit for the position we will contact you soon.

Regards,
{{COMPANY}}

** Please note: Do not reply to this email. This email is sent from an unattended mailbox. Replies will not be read.
